2.0.0.description: IBM Order management Software Professional Edition v10 provides cross-channel order orchestration capabilities to enable intelligent brokering of orders across many disparate systems. It also provides a global view of inventory across the supply chain and enables business users to make changes to order process. For additional details regarding install parameters check [OMS Helm Chart Readme](http://ibm.biz/oms-helm-readme). By installing this product you accept the license terms: [Sterling OMS License Agreement](http://ibm.biz/oms-license) and [Call Center and Store License Agreement](http://ibm.biz/oms-apps-license).
